1.base_formula: =(Crops[[#This Row],[Crop]] & IF(NOT(Crops[[#This Row],[Variety]] = "General"), " (" & Crops[[#This Row],[Variety]] &")", "") & " - " & Crops[[#This Row],[Product]] & " " & Crops[[#This Row],[Seeds Per Planting]] & "X" & IF(Crops[[#This Row],[CACA]], " ext","")) & " | " & Crops[[#This Row],[Growing Structure]] & " " & Crops[[#This Row],[Planting Method]] & " " & Crops[[#This Row],[Seasons]]

16.base_formula: =IF(OR(Crops[[#This Row],[Days in Cells]]="",Crops[[#This Row],[Days in Cells]]=0), "DS","TP")

22.base_formula: = IF(Crops[[#This Row],[Sp]], "Sp", "") & IF(Crops[[#This Row],[Su]], "Su", "") & IF(Crops[[#This Row],[Fa]], "Fa", "") & IF(Crops[[#This Row],[Wi]], "Wi", "") & IF(Crops[[#This Row],[OW]], "Ow","")

35.base_formula: =IFERROR(Crops[[#This Row],[Plantings Per Bed]]*Crops[[#This Row],[Seeds Per Planting]]*Crops[[#This Row],[Safety Factor]]*Crops[[#This Row],[Seeding Factor]],"")

39.base_formula: =SUM(Crops[[#This Row],[Tray 1 Days]],Crops[[#This Row],[Tray 2 Days]],Crops[[#This Row],[Tray 3 Days]])

47.base_formula: =Crops[[#This Row],[STH]]-Crops[[#This Row],[Days in Cells]]+Crops[[#This Row],[Harvest window]]

52.base_formula: =IFERROR(IF(Crops[[#This Row],[Tray 1 Days]]=0,"",Crops[[#This Row],[Plantings Per Bed]]/Crops[[#This Row],[Tray 1 Size]]*Crops[[#This Row],[Safety Factor]]),"")

55.base_formula: =IFERROR(IF(Crops[[#This Row],[Tray 2 Days]]=0,"",Crops[[#This Row],[Plantings Per Bed]]/Crops[[#This Row],[Tray 2 Size]]*Crops[[#This Row],[Safety Factor]]),"")

57.base_formula: =IF(NOT(ISBLANK(Crops[[#This Row],[Tray 3 Size]])), Crops[[#This Row],[Days in Cells Old]]-SUM(Crops[[#This Row],[Tray 1 Days]],Crops[[#This Row],[Tray 2 Days]]), "")

58.base_formula: =IFERROR(IF(Crops[[#This Row],[Tray 3 Days]]=0,"",Crops[[#This Row],[Plantings Per Bed]]/Crops[[#This Row],[Tray 3 Size]]*Crops[[#This Row],[Safety Factor]]),"")

69.base_formula: =Crops[[#This Row],[Custom Yield Per Bed]]*Crops[[#This Row],[Direct Price]]

72.base_formula: =IFERROR(Crops[[#This Row],[Direct Revenue Per Bed]]/Crops[[#This Row],[Days In Field]],-1)

75.base_formula: =Crops[[#This Row],[Target Sewing Date]]+Crops[[#This Row],[Days in Cells]]

82.base_formula: =IF(Crops[[#This Row],[Days in Cells]]<=0,0,Crops[[#This Row],[Plantings Per Bed]]/StartsPerHourSeeding+Crops[[#This Row],[Tray 1 Count]]*5/60)

83.base_formula: =IF(ISBLANK(Crops[[#This Row],[Tray 2 Days]]),0,Crops[[#This Row],[Plantings Per Bed]]/UpPottingPerHour)+IF(Crops[[#This Row],[Tray 3 Days]]="",0,Crops[[#This Row],[Plantings Per Bed]]/UpPottingPerHour)

85.base_formula: =0.5/16*MAX(Crops[[#This Row],[Tray 1 Count]],Crops[[#This Row],[Tray 2 Count]],Crops[[#This Row],[Tray 3 Count]])

86.base_formula: =IF(Crops[[#This Row],[Days in Cells]]>0,IF(IF(Crops[[#This Row],[Tray 3 Size]]>0,Crops[[#This Row],[Tray 3 Size]],IF(Crops[[#This Row],[Tray 2 Size]]>0,Crops[[#This Row],[Tray 2 Size]],Crops[[#This Row],[Tray 1 Size]]))<=18,LargeTransplantTime,SmallTransplantTime)*Crops[[#This Row],[Plantings Per Bed]],0)

95.base_formula: =_xlfn.XLOOKUP(Crops[[#This Row],[Crop]]&Crops[[#This Row],[Product]]&Crops[[#This Row],[Unit]],Products[ID],Products[Marketing (hr)])*Crops[[#This Row],[Direct Revenue Per Bed]]/2000

96.base_formula: =_xlfn.XLOOKUP(Crops[[#This Row],[Crop]]&Crops[[#This Row],[Product]]&Crops[[#This Row],[Unit]],Products[ID],Products[Harvest (s)])*Crops[[#This Row],[Custom Yield Per Bed]]/3600

97.base_formula: =_xlfn.XLOOKUP(Crops[[#This Row],[Crop]]&Crops[[#This Row],[Product]]&Crops[[#This Row],[Unit]],Products[ID],Products[Bunch (s)])*Crops[[#This Row],[Custom Yield Per Bed]]/3600

98.base_formula: =_xlfn.XLOOKUP(Crops[[#This Row],[Crop]]&Crops[[#This Row],[Product]]&Crops[[#This Row],[Unit]],Products[ID],Products[Haul (s)])*Crops[[#This Row],[Custom Yield Per Bed]]/3600

99.base_formula: =_xlfn.XLOOKUP(Crops[[#This Row],[Crop]]&Crops[[#This Row],[Product]]&Crops[[#This Row],[Unit]],Products[ID],Products[Wash (s)])*Crops[[#This Row],[Custom Yield Per Bed]]/3600

100.base_formula: =_xlfn.XLOOKUP(Crops[[#This Row],[Crop]]&Crops[[#This Row],[Product]]&Crops[[#This Row],[Unit]],Products[ID],Products[Condition (s)])*Crops[[#This Row],[Custom Yield Per Bed]]/3600

101.base_formula: =_xlfn.XLOOKUP(Crops[[#This Row],[Crop]]&Crops[[#This Row],[Product]]&Crops[[#This Row],[Unit]],Products[ID],Products[Trim (s)])*Crops[[#This Row],[Custom Yield Per Bed]]/3600

102.base_formula: =_xlfn.XLOOKUP(Crops[[#This Row],[Crop]]&Crops[[#This Row],[Product]]&Crops[[#This Row],[Unit]],Products[ID],Products[Pack (s)])*Crops[[#This Row],[Custom Yield Per Bed]]/3600

103.base_formula: =_xlfn.XLOOKUP(Crops[[#This Row],[Crop]]&Crops[[#This Row],[Product]]&Crops[[#This Row],[Unit]],Products[ID],Products[Clean (s)])*Crops[[#This Row],[Custom Yield Per Bed]]/3600

104.base_formula: =_xlfn.XLOOKUP(Crops[[#This Row],[Crop]]&Crops[[#This Row],[Product]]&Crops[[#This Row],[Unit]],Products[ID],Products[Rehandle (s)])*Crops[[#This Row],[Custom Yield Per Bed]]/3600

105.base_formula: =_xlfn.XLOOKUP(Crops[[#This Row],[Crop]]&Crops[[#This Row],[Product]]&Crops[[#This Row],[Unit]],Products[ID],Products[Market Transport (s)])*Crops[[#This Row],[Custom Yield Per Bed]]/3600

106.base_formula: =_xlfn.XLOOKUP(Crops[[#This Row],[Crop]]&Crops[[#This Row],[Product]]&Crops[[#This Row],[Unit]],Products[ID],Products[Market Transport (s)])*Crops[[#This Row],[Custom Yield Per Bed]]/3600

109.base_formula: =_xlfn.AGGREGATE(9,6,Crops[[#This Row],[Bed Prep]:[Remove Crop Residue]])-0.75*Crops[[#This Row],[Market & Sell]]

110.base_formula: =Crops[[#This Row],[Direct Revenue Per Bed2]]/Crops[[#This Row],[Direct Time]]

111.base_formula: =_xlfn.XLOOKUP(Crops[[#This Row],[ProductIndex]],Products[ID],Products[Packaging Cost])*(Crops[[#This Row],[Custom Yield Per Bed]]/_xlfn.XLOOKUP(Crops[[#This Row],[ProductIndex]],Products[ID],Products[Units Per Pack]))

117.base_formula: =IFERROR(Crops[[#This Row],[Custom Yield Per Bed]]*Crops[[#This Row],[Direct Price]],"")

120.base_formula: =Crops[[#This Row],[Direct Labor Cost]]+Crops[[#This Row],[Direct Non-Labor Cost]]

121.base_formula: =Crops[[#This Row],[Direct Revenue Per Bed2]]-Crops[[#This Row],[Direct Total Cost]]

126.header: Direct Profit Per Owner Labor Hour
126.base_formula: =(Crops[[#This Row],[Direct Revenue Per Bed2]]-Crops[[#This Row],[Direct Non-Labor Cost]])/Crops[[#This Row],[Direct Time]]

127.base_formula: =IFERROR(Crops[[#This Row],[Custom Yield Per Bed]]*Crops[[#This Row],[Rough Wholesale Price]],"")

130.base_formula: =Crops[[#This Row],[Wholesale Labor Cost]]+Crops[[#This Row],[Wholesale Non-Labor Cost]]

131.base_formula: =Crops[[#This Row],[Wholesale Revenue Per Bed]]-Crops[[#This Row],[Wholesale Total Cost]]

136.header: Wholesale Profit Per Owner Labor Hour
136.base_formula: =(Crops[[#This Row],[Wholesale Revenue Per Bed]]-Crops[[#This Row],[Wholesale Non-Labor Cost]])/Crops[[#This Row],[Direct Time]]

137.base_formula: =Crops[[#This Row],[Packaging Costs]]/Crops[[#This Row],[Wholesale Revenue Per Bed]]

141.base_formula: =Crops[[#This Row],[Units Per Harvest]]/Crops[[#This Row],[Days Between Harvest]]*7

143.base_formula: =Crops[[#This Row],[Units Per Harvest]]/Crops[[#This Row],[Days Between Harvest]]*7/_xlfn.XLOOKUP(Crops[[#This Row],[ProductIndex]],Products[ID],Products[CSA Portion])

151.base_formula: =Crops[[#This Row],[Custom Yield Per Bed]]/(Crops[[#This Row],[CSA Need]]*(_xlfn.XLOOKUP(Crops[[#This Row],[ProductIndex]],Products[ID],Products[CSA Portion])*CSAMembers))

152.base_formula: =_xlfn.XLOOKUP(Crops[[#This Row],[ProductIndex]],Products[ID],Products[CSA Portion])*CSAMembers*Crops[[#This Row],[CSA Need]]/Crops[[#This Row],[Custom Yield Per Bed]]
